here is column name with actual name
mjrnl_trtyp: Journal Type
mjrnl_trnno: Journal No
mjrnl_trdat: Journal Date
mjrnl_refno: Journal Ref No
mjrnl_narrt: Journal Narrations
mjrnl_drval: Total DR value
mjrnl_crval: Total CR Value
djrnl_drval: Line DR value
djrnl_crval: Line CR Value
djrnl_descr: Line Narrations
chtac_ccode: Chart of Accounts
chtac_cname: Chart of Accounts Name
chtac_ctype: Chart of Accounts Types (top 5)
chtac_chtno: Chart of Accounts No
party_ptype: Sub Ledger Type/Source
party_pcode: Sub Ledger Code
party_pname: Sub Ledger Name

